@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lphbim(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.abs(wp.cos(v0 + 0.98)))
    v0 = (v1 + (wp.abs(v0 + 0.75) / v2))
    tmp = (wp.sin(wp.abs(v0 + 0.40)) / ((v0 + 0.81 * v0 + 0.52) - wp.abs(v0 + 0.21)))
    v0 = 0.52
    tmp = v0
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.cos((tmp + 0.90 * v2 + 0.18)))
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.cos(v2 + 0.09)) - (wp.cos(v1 + 0.76) / (v1 + 0.25 + v2 + 0.36)))
    data[tid] = v0
